{"tid":1090400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊咩行姐，返多份工好過啦","createTime":"2019-04-03T12:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T13:09:17.000Z","uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"738e565dd5f36b659d6bb0ffbf1bc760875edbb9","tid":1090400,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"可能講中香港人個心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年佔中同之前，啲後生仔好有heart，成日話不滿政府就去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佔中後物價越來越高，樓價越升越有，打份牛工都跑輸通脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是星期日越來越少人話要上街，政府施政又越來越唔掂，七一都少咗人上街，點解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係窮呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屎都冇得食呀，唔返多份工邊有錢結婚買樓養家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5e451ae5f6f7268f0ed333f7fc8a39f2d29399","tid":1090400,"uid":28523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"其實係心淡"},{"pid":"759ac698eda410e3eead1b55d972bdf7b61c531a","tid":1090400,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e5e451ae5f6f7268f0ed333f7fc8a39f2d29399","tid":1090400,"uid":28523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"其實係心淡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔覺喎，啲人屌得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a2b1029c3fc0f4df35df4d640d67b2d6819822","tid":1090400,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"以前十個屌可能都有1個出街<br />\nE家100個屌可能得1個"},{"pid":"60332e418cceed8e4e5bbdaa423476ef2c13e3bd","tid":1090400,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor